Sound License
=============

All audio files in this directory are procedurally generated sine-wave
beeps created specifically for the FitForge project.

These sounds are original works with no third-party source material.
They are released under the same MIT license as the rest of this project.

Generated using Python's `wave` module — pure sine-wave tones at
22050 Hz sample rate, 16-bit mono.

Files:
  beep_high.wav  — Ascending double beep (880 Hz + 1100 Hz)
  beep_low.wav   — Single low tone (440 Hz)
  tick.wav       — Short tick (1000 Hz)
  complete.wav   — Triple ascending beep (880 + 1100 + 1320 Hz)
  warning.wav    — Two rapid beeps (1000 Hz)
